relevant_findings.general: Well-appearing, comfortable, in no apparent distress (NAD)
relevant_findings.HEENT: Atraumatic/Normocephalic (AT/NC), Pupils Equal, Round, Reactive to Light (PERRL), Extraocular Movements Intact (EOMI), anicteric sclera, dry mucous membranes (MM)
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm (RRR), S1/S2 present, no murmurs, gallops, or rubs
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally (CTAB), no wheezes, rales, rhonchi, breathing comfortably without use of accessory muscles
relevant_findings.gastrointestinal: Soft, nondistended, nontender in all quadrants, no rebound/guarding, no hepatosplenomegaly
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert, moving all 4 extremities with purpose, face symmetric
relevant_findings.dermatological: Warm and well perfused, no excoriations or lesions, no rashes
